Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.49,0:01:29.99,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\c&H9262F8&\fn@方正隶变_GBK\frz270\pos(18,540)\fscy100\fscx110\fsp0}我{\c&HDFC73A&}喜{\c}欢你哦
